{"title":"Jacob Jameson","markdown":{"yaml":{"title":"Jacob Jameson","image":"../images/profile.png","about":{"template":"trestles","image-width":"13em","image-shape":"round","links":[{"icon":"rss","text":"blog","href":"https://jacobjameson.com/posts/blog"},{"icon":"envelope","text":"email","href":"mailto:jacobjameson@g.harvard.edu"},{"icon":"github","text":"github","href":"https://github.com/jacobjameson"},{"icon":"twitter","text":"twitter","href":"https://twitter.com/JacobCJameson"},{"icon":"mortarboard","text":"cv","href":"/Data/Jameson_vitae.pdf"},{"icon":"book","text":"scholar","href":"https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=jIrUgQsAAAAJ&hl=en"},{"icon":"film","text":"letterboxd","href":"https://letterboxd.com/jacobjameson/"}]},"from":"markdown+emoji","comments":false,"page-layout":"full"},"headingText":"whoami","containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n<div class=\"prompt-line\"><span class=\"ps1\">jacobjameson</span>@<span class=\"host\">harvard</span>:~$<span class=\"cursor\"></span></div>\n\n\n<div class=\"hero-subtitle\">phd candidate &nbsp;·&nbsp; health policy &amp; decision sciences &nbsp;·&nbsp; harvard university</div>\n\nI develop methods in [causal inference](research.qmd), Bayesian statistics, and reinforcement learning to improve decision-making in health and public policy. I am a National Institute of Mental Health (NIMH) funded Predoctoral Research Fellow in [Comparative Effectiveness Research for Suicide Prevention](https://causalab.sph.harvard.edu/suicideprevention/) at [Brigham and Women's Hospital](https://www.brighamandwomens.org), with applications to suicide prevention, emergency department operations, and precision medicine.\n\nI also care deeply about [teaching](teaching.qmd) — I have worked with students at Harvard, UChicago Medicine, and as a Teach For America corps member in New Haven Public Schools.\n\n<div class=\"tag-row\">\n<span class=\"tag\">--causal-inference</span>\n<span class=\"tag\">--reinforcement-learning</span>\n<span class=\"tag\">--bayesian-stats</span>\n</div>\n\n## cat news.log\n\n<div class=\"news-item\">\n<div class=\"news-date\">2026-03</div>\n<div class=\"news-text\"><span class=\"news-flag\">new</span>Selected (29/132) for the <a href=\"https://sites.google.com/umich.edu/isye-mse-ioe-joint-rising-star/home\">2026 IOE-ISyE-MS&E Rising Stars Workshop</a>.</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"news-item\">\n<div class=\"news-date\">2026-03</div>\n<div class=\"news-text\"><span class=\"news-flag\">new</span>Finalist in Harvard's <a href=\"https://gsas.harvard.edu/academics/writing/three-minute-thesis\">Three Minute Thesis (3MT®) Competition</a>.</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"news-item\">\n<div class=\"news-date\">2025-09</div>\n<div class=\"news-text\">Finalist, <a href=\"https://connect.informs.org/discussion/finalists-of-the-2025-informs-has-best-student-paper-competition\">INFORMS HAS Best Student Paper Competition</a> — <a href=\"/Data/INFORMS Award 2025.pdf\">Honorable Mention</a>.</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"news-item\">\n<div class=\"news-date\">2025-06</div>\n<div class=\"news-text\"><a href=\"/Data/Distinction Award 2025.pdf\">Distinction in Student Teaching</a>, Harvard Kennedy School.</div>\n</div>\n\n---\n\n<details>\n<summary>show earlier entries</summary>\n\n<div class=\"news-item\">\n<div class=\"news-date\">2024-05</div>\n<div class=\"news-text\"><a href=\"/Data/Distinction Award 2024.pdf\">Distinction in Student Teaching</a> and the <a href=\"https://www.hks.harvard.edu/more/about/leadership-administration/academic-deans-office/slate/research-and-innovation/making/teaching#recipients\">Dean's Award for Excellence in Student Teaching</a>, Harvard Kennedy School. <a href=\"https://chds.hsph.harvard.edu/jameson-wins-student-teaching-award/\">↗</a></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"news-item\">\n<div class=\"news-date\">2024-05</div>\n<div class=\"news-text\">NIMH T32 Predoctoral Fellowship — <a href=\"https://causalab.sph.harvard.edu/suicideprevention/\">Comparative Effectiveness Research for Suicide Risk Prevention</a>.</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"news-item\">\n<div class=\"news-date\">2024-02</div>\n<div class=\"news-text\"><a href=\"https://chds.hsph.harvard.edu/chds-welcomes-new-educational-innovation-scholar/\">Center for Health Decision Science Educational Innovation Scholar</a>.</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"news-item\">\n<div class=\"news-date\">2024-02</div>\n<div class=\"news-text\"><a href=\"https://chds.hsph.harvard.edu/2024-raiffa-fund-awards/\">2024 Howard Raiffa Award</a>, Harvard Center for Risk Analysis.</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"news-item\">\n<div class=\"news-date\">2023-09</div>\n<div class=\"news-text\">Finalist, <a href=\"https://connect.informs.org/discussion/psor-best-paper-and-best-video-competition-results\">INFORMS Public Sector OR Best Video Award</a> — <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=do6j8G9qUoM\">Improving Emergency Department Flow</a>.</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"news-item\">\n<div class=\"news-date\">2023-01</div>\n<div class=\"news-text\"><a href=\"https://chds.hsph.harvard.edu/jameson-receives-raiffa-award/\">2023 Howard Raiffa Award</a>, Harvard Center for Risk Analysis.</div>\n</div>\n\n</details>\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n\n<div class=\"prompt-line\"><span class=\"ps1\">jacobjameson</span>@<span class=\"host\">harvard</span>:~$<span class=\"cursor\"></span></div>\n\n## whoami\n\n<div class=\"hero-subtitle\">phd candidate &nbsp;·&nbsp; health policy &amp; decision sciences &nbsp;·&nbsp; harvard university</div>\n\nI develop methods in [causal inference](research.qmd), Bayesian statistics, and reinforcement learning to improve decision-making in health and public policy. I am a National Institute of Mental Health (NIMH) funded Predoctoral Research Fellow in [Comparative Effectiveness Research for Suicide Prevention](https://causalab.sph.harvard.edu/suicideprevention/) at [Brigham and Women's Hospital](https://www.brighamandwomens.org), with applications to suicide prevention, emergency department operations, and precision medicine.\n\nI also care deeply about [teaching](teaching.qmd) — I have worked with students at Harvard, UChicago Medicine, and as a Teach For America corps member in New Haven Public Schools.\n\n<div class=\"tag-row\">\n<span class=\"tag\">--causal-inference</span>\n<span class=\"tag\">--reinforcement-learning</span>\n<span class=\"tag\">--bayesian-stats</span>\n</div>\n\n## cat news.log\n\n<div class=\"news-item\">\n<div class=\"news-date\">2026-03</div>\n<div class=\"news-text\"><span class=\"news-flag\">new</span>Selected (29/132) for the <a href=\"https://sites.google.com/umich.edu/isye-mse-ioe-joint-rising-star/home\">2026 IOE-ISyE-MS&E Rising Stars Workshop</a>.</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"news-item\">\n<div class=\"news-date\">2026-03</div>\n<div class=\"news-text\"><span class=\"news-flag\">new</span>Finalist in Harvard's <a href=\"https://gsas.harvard.edu/academics/writing/three-minute-thesis\">Three Minute Thesis (3MT®) Competition</a>.</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"news-item\">\n<div class=\"news-date\">2025-09</div>\n<div class=\"news-text\">Finalist, <a href=\"https://connect.informs.org/discussion/finalists-of-the-2025-informs-has-best-student-paper-competition\">INFORMS HAS Best Student Paper Competition</a> — <a href=\"/Data/INFORMS Award 2025.pdf\">Honorable Mention</a>.</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"news-item\">\n<div class=\"news-date\">2025-06</div>\n<div class=\"news-text\"><a href=\"/Data/Distinction Award 2025.pdf\">Distinction in Student Teaching</a>, Harvard Kennedy School.</div>\n</div>\n\n---\n\n<details>\n<summary>show earlier entries</summary>\n\n<div class=\"news-item\">\n<div class=\"news-date\">2024-05</div>\n<div class=\"news-text\"><a href=\"/Data/Distinction Award 2024.pdf\">Distinction in Student Teaching</a> and the <a href=\"https://www.hks.harvard.edu/more/about/leadership-administration/academic-deans-office/slate/research-and-innovation/making/teaching#recipients\">Dean's Award for Excellence in Student Teaching</a>, Harvard Kennedy School. <a href=\"https://chds.hsph.harvard.edu/jameson-wins-student-teaching-award/\">↗</a></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"news-item\">\n<div class=\"news-date\">2024-05</div>\n<div class=\"news-text\">NIMH T32 Predoctoral Fellowship — <a href=\"https://causalab.sph.harvard.edu/suicideprevention/\">Comparative Effectiveness Research for Suicide Risk Prevention</a>.</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"news-item\">\n<div class=\"news-date\">2024-02</div>\n<div class=\"news-text\"><a href=\"https://chds.hsph.harvard.edu/chds-welcomes-new-educational-innovation-scholar/\">Center for Health Decision Science Educational Innovation Scholar</a>.</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"news-item\">\n<div class=\"news-date\">2024-02</div>\n<div class=\"news-text\"><a href=\"https://chds.hsph.harvard.edu/2024-raiffa-fund-awards/\">2024 Howard Raiffa Award</a>, Harvard Center for Risk Analysis.</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"news-item\">\n<div class=\"news-date\">2023-09</div>\n<div class=\"news-text\">Finalist, <a href=\"https://connect.informs.org/discussion/psor-best-paper-and-best-video-competition-results\">INFORMS Public Sector OR Best Video Award</a> — <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=do6j8G9qUoM\">Improving Emergency Department Flow</a>.</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"news-item\">\n<div class=\"news-date\">2023-01</div>\n<div class=\"news-text\"><a href=\"https://chds.hsph.harvard.edu/jameson-receives-raiffa-award/\">2023 Howard Raiffa Award</a>, Harvard Center for Risk Analysis.</div>\n</div>\n\n</details>\n"},"formats":{"html":{"identifier":{"display-name":"HTML","target-format":"html","base-format":"html"},"execute":{"fig-width":7,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina","fig-dpi":96,"df-print":"default","error":false,"eval":true,"cache":null,"freeze":false,"echo":true,"output":true,"warning":true,"include":true,"keep-md":false,"keep-ipynb":false,"ipynb":null,"enabled":null,"daemon":null,"daemon-restart":false,"debug":false,"ipyn